    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nIf log(a + 3 ) + log(a \u2013 3) = 1 ,then a=?\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\n\u00a0log10((a + 3)(a \u2013 3))=1\nlog10(a2 \u2013 9) = 1\n(a2 \u2013 9) = 10\na2 = 19\na = \u221a19",
